---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Our Story — TógBlocks"
  description="TógBlocks started on a kitchen table in Kildare. A niece, a name, and a 3D printer that never quite switched off. Here's how it happened."
  currentPage="/about"
>

  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
  <div class="ab-hero">
    <div class="ab-hero__studs" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="ab-hero__body">
      <p class="ab-eyebrow">❤️ Family made in Ireland</p>
      <h1 class="ab-hero__title">
        Built on a kitchen&nbsp;table.<br/>
        <em>Grown with love.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="ab-hero__sub">
        <em>Tóg</em> is the Irish for "build." It's also, handily, the start of "together."<br/>
        That's not a coincidence — it's the whole point.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="ab-hero__studs" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <span class="ab-blob ab-blob--1" aria-hidden="true">🏠</span>
    <span class="ab-blob ab-blob--2" aria-hidden="true">🧱</span>
    <span class="ab-blob ab-blob--3" aria-hidden="true">❤️</span>
    <span class="ab-blob ab-blob--4" aria-hidden="true">✨</span>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ ORIGIN STORY ═══ -->
  <section class="ab-origin">
    <div class="wrap ab-origin__inner">

      <!-- left: decorative -->
      <div class="ab-origin__visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="ab-kitchen">
          <div class="ab-kitchen__roof"></div>
          <div class="ab-kitchen__house">
            <div class="ab-kitchen__window"></div>
            <div class="ab-kitchen__door"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ab-kitchen__table">
            <div class="ab-bricks-row">
              <span class="ab-brick ab-brick--red"></span>
              <span class="ab-brick ab-brick--blue"></span>
              <span class="ab-brick ab-brick--yellow"></span>
              <span class="ab-brick ab-brick--red"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="ab-bricks-row ab-bricks-row--2">
              <span class="ab-brick ab-brick--yellow"></span>
              <span class="ab-brick ab-brick--blue"></span>
              <span class="ab-brick ab-brick--red"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ab-printer">
            <div class="ab-printer__body">
              <div class="ab-printer__head"></div>
              <div class="ab-printer__bed"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="ab-printer__label">3D Printer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- right: story -->
      <div class="ab-origin__story">
        <span class="ab-eyebrow-sm">How it all started</span>
        <h2 class="ab-origin__h">She wanted her name above her bed.</h2>
        <p>
          It started with a niece. She wanted her name above her bed — the kind you see in every kids' shop.
          But the shop-bought ones didn't come in her name, and the ones that did looked, well, a bit sad.
        </p>
        <p>
          One evening in our kitchen in <strong>Kildare</strong>, we sat down with a 3D printer,
          a box of second-hand LEGO® baseplates, and a terrible idea that we couldn't let go of.
          By midnight we'd made five letters. By morning, the whole family wanted a set.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="ab-pullquote">
          <span class="ab-pullquote__mark" aria-hidden="true">"</span>
          <p>One evening on a kitchen table. A niece, a name, and a printer that never quite switched off.</p>
        </blockquote>

        <p>
          That was the start of TógBlocks. Now we build names for cots, cakes, desks, and doors
          all over Ireland — every one printed, checked, and boxed by hand. No factory, no middlemen.
          Just us, the printer, and a lot of coloured filament.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ THE PEOPLE ═══ -->
  <section class="ab-people">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">The faces behind the parcels</span>
        <h2>A proper family business —<br/>no corporate nonsense</h2>
        <p>Every order is touched by someone who cares too much about stud alignment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ab-team">

        <div class="ab-person">
          <div class="ab-person__avatar" style="--av-bg:#1D4ED8">
            <span>🖨️</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ab-person__badge">The Maker</div>
          <h3 class="ab-person__name">The 3D Printer Whisperer</h3>
          <p class="ab-person__bio">
            Up at 6am calibrating nozzles. Has strong opinions about layer height
            and knows every brick colour by hex code. Probably needs professional help.
          </p>
          <p class="ab-person__fact">🏆 Personal record: 14 letters printed in one sitting</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ab-person">
          <div class="ab-person__avatar" style="--av-bg:#169B62">
            <span>📦</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ab-person__badge">The Packer</div>
          <h3 class="ab-person__name">Chief of Getting It Out the Door</h3>
          <p class="ab-person__bio">
            Wraps every order like it's going to a birthday party — because it usually is.
            Writes the little notes by hand. Cried once when a "LUCA" set came out perfectly.
          </p>
          <p class="ab-person__fact">✉️ Has written over 200 personal order notes</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ab-person">
          <div class="ab-person__avatar" style="--av-bg:#F59E0B">
            <span>🔍</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ab-person__badge">Quality Control</div>
          <h3 class="ab-person__name">The Sternest Critic (Age 7)</h3>
          <p class="ab-person__bio">
            Self-appointed inspector. Rejects anything that doesn't "click right."
            Responsible for our zero-tolerance policy on wobbly studs.
            Works for biscuits and screen time.
          </p>
          <p class="ab-person__fact">🍪 Current salary: 2 Hobnobs per inspection</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ VALUES ═══ -->
  <section class="ab-values">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">What we care about</span>
        <h2>The things we'd never cut corners on</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="ab-values__grid">

        <div class="ab-value-card ab-value-card--blue">
          <div class="ab-value-card__icon">🇮🇪</div>
          <h3>Printed in Ireland, by us</h3>
          <p>Every single order is printed in our home in Kildare. Not drop-shipped, not outsourced. Us, our printers, your name.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ab-value-card ab-value-card--green">
          <div class="ab-value-card__icon">🧱</div>
          <h3>Keepsakes, not clutter</h3>
          <p>A name that clicks apart and rebuilds — it's a toy and a memento in one. Meant to last years, not until the next bin day.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ab-value-card ab-value-card--yellow">
          <div class="ab-value-card__icon">📬</div>
          <h3>A real person on the email</h3>
          <p>No bots, no ticket systems. When you write to us, you get a reply from one of the two adults who run this thing.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ab-value-card ab-value-card--orange">
          <div class="ab-value-card__icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>3 days, no fuss</h3>
          <p>We print, check, and post within 3 working days. If something's wrong, we fix it. Full stop.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ IRISH CONNECTION ═══ -->
  <section class="ab-irish">
    <div class="ab-irish__studs" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="wrap ab-irish__inner">
      <div class="ab-irish__text">
        <span class="ab-eyebrow-light">A word on the name</span>
        <h2 class="ab-irish__title">
          <em>Tóg</em> — Build.<br/>
          <em>Le chéile</em> — Together.
        </h2>
        <p>
          In Irish, <strong>tóg</strong> means to build, to lift, to raise up.
          It's the word you'd use for raising a child, building a wall, or putting up a name above a door.
          We like that — one word that holds all of that weight at once.
        </p>
        <p>
          And <em>le chéile</em> means together. Because every name we build was chosen by someone
          who loves the person whose name it is. That's the bit that gets us every time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-irish__deco" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="ab-shamrock">
          <span>🍀</span>
          <p class="ab-shamrock__word">TógBlocks</p>
          <p class="ab-shamrock__irish">le grá ó Chill Dara</p>
          <p class="ab-shamrock__english">with love from Kildare</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ab-irish__studs" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ TIMELINE ═══ -->
  <section class="ab-timeline-section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our journey</span>
        <h2>From one niece to Ireland — and beyond</h2>
      </div>
      <ol class="ab-timeline">
        <li class="ab-tl-item">
          <div class="ab-tl-dot ab-tl-dot--1">🏠</div>
          <div class="ab-tl-content">
            <span class="ab-tl-year">The Beginning</span>
            <h3>One kitchen table, one niece, one name</h3>
            <p>Five letters, one baseplate, and the realisation that we'd be doing this for a while.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="ab-tl-item">
          <div class="ab-tl-dot ab-tl-dot--2">🖨️</div>
          <div class="ab-tl-content">
            <span class="ab-tl-year">First orders</span>
            <h3>Friends asked. Then their friends asked.</h3>
            <p>Word spread through WhatsApp, Christmas, and "where did you get that?" moments at birthday parties.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="ab-tl-item">
          <div class="ab-tl-dot ab-tl-dot--3">🌍</div>
          <div class="ab-tl-content">
            <span class="ab-tl-year">Growing up</span>
            <h3>Names across Ireland — and the world</h3>
            <p>From Donegal to Kerry, Cork to Dublin, and then further — parcels heading to the UK, Europe, and beyond. Irish names, English names, names we'd never heard before. Every one a joy to build.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="ab-tl-item">
          <div class="ab-tl-dot ab-tl-dot--4">❤️</div>
          <div class="ab-tl-content">
            <span class="ab-tl-year">Today</span>
            <h3>Still just us. Still just care.</h3>
            <p>Same kitchen. Same printer. Same handwritten notes. We haven't outsourced the love.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CTA ═══ -->
  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="cta-band">
        <div class="studs-deco" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <p class="ab-cta-eyebrow">Ready to build something?</p>
        <h2>Put a name on it.</h2>
        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);max-width:42ch;margin:0 auto 28px;font-size:var(--fs-md)">
          Takes about a minute. We'll print it, pack it with care, and have it at your door within 3&nbsp;days.
        </p>
        <a class="btn btn--cta btn--lg" href="/builder">Start building →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
/* ── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.ab-hero {
  position: relative;
  background: var(--green-deep);
  color: var(--white);
  text-align: center;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.ab-hero__studs {
  height: 36px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.20);
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, var(--orange) 44%, transparent 45%);
  background-size: 36px 36px;
  background-position: 18px 4px;
  background-repeat: repeat-x;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.ab-hero__body {
  padding: clamp(40px, 7vw, 88px) var(--gutter);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 18px;
}

.ab-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: var(--fs-sm);
  letter-spacing: .07em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--orange);
  animation: abPopUp .45s var(--ease-pop) both;
}

.ab-hero__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 1.8rem + 2.5vw, 4rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--white);
  margin: 0;
  animation: abPopUp .5s var(--ease-pop) .08s both;
}

.ab-hero__title em {
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--orange);
  display: inline-block;
  animation: gentleWobble 5s ease-in-out infinite 1.5s;
}

@keyframes gentleWobble {
  0%, 80%, 100% { transform: none; }
  85%  { transform: rotate(-2deg) scale(1.03); }
  92%  { transform: rotate(2deg) scale(1.03); }
}

.ab-hero__sub {
  font-size: var(--fs-md);
  opacity: .85;
  max-width: 520px;
  line-height: var(--lh-normal);
  margin: 0;
  animation: abPopUp .55s var(--ease-pop) .16s both;
}

.ab-hero__sub em { color: var(--orange); font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; }

@keyframes abPopUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px) scale(.97); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
}

/* floating blobs */
.ab-blob {
  position: absolute;
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  opacity: .15;
  pointer-events: none;
  user-select: none;
}
.ab-blob--1 { top: 22%; left:  4%; animation: blobDrift 6.0s ease-in-out infinite; }
.ab-blob--2 { top: 65%; left:  9%; animation: blobDrift 7.5s ease-in-out infinite .7s; }
.ab-blob--3 { top: 20%; right: 6%; animation: blobDrift 5.5s ease-in-out infinite 1.2s; }
.ab-blob--4 { top: 72%; right: 4%; animation: blobDrift 8.0s ease-in-out infinite .3s; }

@keyframes blobDrift {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(-6deg); }
  50%       { transform: translateY(-16px) rotate(6deg); }
}

/* ── ORIGIN STORY ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.ab-origin {
  padding-block: clamp(52px, 7vw, 96px);
  background: var(--white);
}

.ab-origin__inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
  gap: clamp(32px, 6vw, 80px);
  align-items: center;
}

@media (max-width: 760px) {
  .ab-origin__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .ab-origin__visual { order: 2; }
}

/* CSS kitchen scene */
.ab-kitchen {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 32px;
  background: var(--green-soft);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  border: 2px solid var(--line);
  min-height: 360px;
  justify-content: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.ab-kitchen::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, var(--line) 42%, transparent 43%);
  background-size: 24px 24px;
  opacity: .3;
}

.ab-kitchen__roof {
  width: 0;
  height: 0;
  border-left: 60px solid transparent;
  border-right: 60px solid transparent;
  border-bottom: 50px solid var(--green-deep);
  opacity: .8;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.ab-kitchen__house {
  width: 120px;
  height: 90px;
  background: var(--white);
  border: 2px solid var(--line-strong);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: space-around;
  padding: 10px;
}

.ab-kitchen__window {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  background: var(--sage);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
  border: 2px solid var(--sage);
  position: absolute;
  top: 16px;
  left: 14px;
}

.ab-kitchen__door {
  width: 24px;
  height: 36px;
  background: var(--orange);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xs) var(--radius-xs) 0 0;
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  right: 14px;
}

.ab-kitchen__table {
  background: var(--cream-deep);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: 12px 16px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
  align-items: center;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.ab-bricks-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 6px;
}

.ab-brick {
  width: 28px;
  height: 20px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-brick);
  position: relative;
  display: block;
  animation: brickBounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.ab-brick--red    { background: var(--brick-red);    animation-delay: 0s; }
.ab-brick--blue   { background: var(--brick-blue);   animation-delay: .2s; }
.ab-brick--yellow { background: var(--brick-yellow); animation-delay: .4s; }

.ab-brick::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -6px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 14px;
  height: 7px;
  border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0;
  background: inherit;
  filter: brightness(1.1);
}

@keyframes brickBounce {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50%       { transform: translateY(-4px); }
}

.ab-bricks-row--2 { opacity: .7; }

.ab-printer {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.ab-printer__body {
  width: 52px;
  background: var(--ink);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: 6px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 4px;
}

.ab-printer__head {
  height: 8px;
  background: var(--sage);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
  animation: printerScan 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.ab-printer__bed {
  height: 14px;
  background: var(--white);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
  opacity: .7;
}

@keyframes printerScan {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) scaleX(.5); opacity: .6; }
  50%       { transform: translateX(50%)  scaleX(.5); opacity: 1;  }
}

.ab-printer__label {
  font-size: var(--fs-xs);
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ink-60);
}

/* story text */
.ab-eyebrow-sm {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: var(--fs-xs);
  letter-spacing: .08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--green);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.ab-origin__h {
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 1.3rem + 1.5vw, 2.4rem);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  line-height: var(--lh-snug);
}

.ab-origin__story p {
  font-size: var(--fs-md);
  line-height: var(--lh-normal);
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.ab-pullquote {
  margin: 28px 0;
  padding: 20px 24px;
  background: var(--orange-soft);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);
  border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0;
  position: relative;
}

.ab-pullquote__mark {
  position: absolute;
  top: -10px;
  left: 16px;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 4rem;
  color: var(--orange);
  line-height: 1;
  opacity: .4;
}

.ab-pullquote p {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: var(--fs-lg);
  color: var(--green-deep);
  line-height: var(--lh-snug);
  margin: 0;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

/* ── PEOPLE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.ab-people {
  padding-block: clamp(48px, 6vw, 88px);
  background: var(--offwhite);
}

.ab-team {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: clamp(16px, 2.5vw, 28px);
}

@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .ab-team { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 400px; margin-inline: auto; }
}

.ab-person {
  background: var(--white);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--line);
  padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 32px);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
  text-align: center;
  transition: transform .2s var(--ease-pop), box-shadow .2s ease;
}

.ab-person:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
}

.ab-person__avatar {
  width: 72px;
  height: 72px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--av-bg, var(--green-deep));
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin: 0 auto;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px -6px color-mix(in srgb, var(--av-bg) 60%, transparent);
  animation: floatAvatar 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.ab-person:nth-child(2) .ab-person__avatar { animation-delay: -1.3s; }
.ab-person:nth-child(3) .ab-person__avatar { animation-delay: -2.6s; }

@keyframes floatAvatar {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50%       { transform: translateY(-6px); }
}

.ab-person__badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: var(--fs-xs);
  padding: 3px 12px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  background: var(--orange);
  color: var(--ink);
  align-self: center;
}

.ab-person__name {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--fs-base);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: var(--lh-snug);
  margin: 0;
}

.ab-person__bio {
  font-size: var(--fs-sm);
  color: var(--ink-60);
  line-height: var(--lh-normal);
  margin: 0;
}

.ab-person__fact {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: var(--fs-xs);
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--green);
  padding: 6px 12px;
  background: var(--green-soft);
  border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
}

/* ── VALUES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.ab-values {
  padding-block: clamp(48px, 6vw, 88px);
  background: var(--white);
}

.ab-values__grid {
  display: grid;
